| Specification type   | Specification                            | Reason                              | Testing method                   |
|----------------------|------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------|----------------------------------|
| Introduction         | Clearly state the AI's objective and initial setup | Sets a clear context for viewers    | Verify clarity and completeness  |
|----------------------|------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------|----------------------------------|
| Baseline Performance | Display initial untrained AI behavior    | Establishes a baseline for progress | Compare initial and final behaviors |
|----------------------|------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------|----------------------------------|
| Learning Process     | Annotate significant learning moments    | Highlights key learning phases      | Check for clear annotations      |
|----------------------|------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------|----------------------------------|
| Visual Indicators    | Use heat maps, path traces, overlays     | Illustrates AI's decision-making    | Review visual clarity            |
|----------------------|------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------|----------------------------------|
| Challenges           | Include AI's mistakes and adjustments    | Shows the iterative learning process | Check for coverage of failures   |
|----------------------|------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------|----------------------------------|
| Progressive Improvement | Side-by-side comparisons of AI behavior | Demonstrates learning progress    | Verify comparison accuracy       |
|----------------------|------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------|----------------------------------|
| Final Performance    | Show the AI achieving its objectives     | Concludes the learning journey      | Validate against initial goals   |
|----------------------|------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------|----------------------------------|
| Narration            | Add voice-over or subtitles              | Guides viewers through the video    | Verify script clarity and synchronization |
|----------------------|------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------|----------------------------------|
| Conclusion           | Summarize key points and future directions | Wraps up the video effectively    | Check for a comprehensive summary |
|----------------------|------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------|----------------------------------|
| Dynamic Elements     | Include engaging visual elements         | Keeps viewers engaged               | Test for engagement and flow     |
